data.description: Located on a beautiful block in West Pullman, this two-story home has limitless potential. It offers five bedrooms, two baths (One bathroom recently remodeled), a recently remodeled kitchen, a living room, a dining room, a patio, and a full basement. The owner also has a 3,075 sqft lot next to the home. This lot is not included in the price. This lot can be purchased for an additional amount.
